1947;;Cry Wolf;;American;;Peter Godfrey;;Errol Flynn, Barbara Stanwyck;;mystery;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cry_Wolf_(1947_film);;Sandra Marshall, the widow of the owner of a remote mansion, arrives to take charge and claim the inheritance of her late husband. She receives a cold reception, especially from research scientist Mark Caldwell, who seems to be keeping her sister-in-law, Julie, a virtual prisoner in the house.